Wani faifan bidiyo da ke yawo a kafafen sada zumunta na yanar gizo ya yi ikirarin cewa wasu ‘yan bindiga sun kai hari wani cocin Celestial da ke Owo, jihar Ondo. “Zuciyata na zubar da jini, ‘yan bindiga sun kai hari cocin Celestial jiya ma a jihar Ondo,” in ji ta bakin wani ɗan gajeren bidiyo da Florence Omojesu, mai amfani da TikTok, ta saka kwana guda bayan harin cocin Katolika. <img class="alignnone wp-image-715699 size-full" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/WhatsApp-Image-2022-06-23-at-10.18.55-AM-e1655976771328.jpeg" alt="" width="485" height="958" srcset="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/WhatsApp-Image-2022-06-23-at-10.18.55-AM-e1655976771328.jpeg 485w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/WhatsApp-Image-2022-06-23-at-10.18.55-AM-e1655976771328-152x300.jpeg 152w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/WhatsApp-Image-2022-06-23-at-10.18.55-AM-e1655976771328-12x24.jpeg 12w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/WhatsApp-Image-2022-06-23-at-10.18.55-AM-e1655976771328-18x36.jpeg 18w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/WhatsApp-Image-2022-06-23-at-10.18.55-AM-e1655976771328-24x48.jpeg 24w" sizes="(max-width: 485px) 100vw, 485px" /> Bidiyon ya fara yawo a yanar gizo bayan harin da ya yi sanadin salwantar rayukan mabiya coci a Owo a ranar Lahadi, 5 ga watan Yuni. “Wani harin Fulani ne a wani cocin Celestial da ke Akure,” in ji taken wani faifan bidiyon TikTok, wanda wani Ebenezer Anu ya wallafa, kamar yadda aka yada a WhatsApp. <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-715702" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/WhatsApp-Image-2022-06-23-at-10.07.48-AM-1-e1655977135156.jpeg" alt="" width="480" height="850" srcset="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/WhatsApp-Image-2022-06-23-at-10.07.48-AM-1-e1655977135156.jpeg 480w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/WhatsApp-Image-2022-06-23-at-10.07.48-AM-1-e1655977135156-169x300.jpeg 169w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/WhatsApp-Image-2022-06-23-at-10.07.48-AM-1-e1655977135156-14x24.jpeg 14w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/WhatsApp-Image-2022-06-23-at-10.07.48-AM-1-e1655977135156-20x36.jpeg 20w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/WhatsApp-Image-2022-06-23-at-10.07.48-AM-1-e1655977135156-27x48.jpeg 27w" sizes="(max-width: 480px) 100vw, 480px" /> Bidiyon na dakika 13 ya dauki wani gini da aka zana da fari da shudi. Haka kuma an nuna mata da yara sanye da fararen riguna na addini masu kwarara da hula. A cikin faifan bidiyon, ana iya ganin wata mata dauke da yaro a gefenta, duk da haka tana rike da wani da hannu, duk da cewa sun yi taho-mu-gama. Wata muryar mace tana kururuwa cikin harshen Yarbanci, “Ba za mu iya komawa gida ba, a ina za mu ɓuya? Yesu!” za a iya ji a bayan bidiyon da ke nuna bala’i. A Facebook, bidiyon ya tattara ra’ayoyi sama da 8,100. An kuma buga a Twitter. <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-715706" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Celestial-Church-Owo-.jpg" alt="" width="808" height="547" srcset="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Celestial-Church-Owo-.jpg 808w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Celestial-Church-Owo--300x203.jpg 300w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Celestial-Church-Owo--768x520.jpg 768w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Celestial-Church-Owo--24x16.jpg 24w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Celestial-Church-Owo--36x24.jpg 36w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Celestial-Church-Owo--48x32.jpg 48w" sizes="(max-width: 808px) 100vw, 808px" /> Fage. A ranar Lahadi, 5 ga watan Yuni, wasu ‘yan bindiga sun kai hari cocin St. Francis Catholic Church a karamar hukumar Owo ta jihar Ondo. Hadarin dai yayi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane da dama tare da jikkata wasu da dama. An kuma kashe yara a harin da aka kai a harabar cocin. A ranar 17 ga watan Yuni, an gudanar da jana’izar jama’a ga masu ibada 40 da aka kashe a harin. Tabbatarwa TheCable ta tuntubi Fumilayo Odunlami jami’in hulda da jama’a na ‘yan sanda a Ondo domin tabbatar da harin da ake zargin an kai wa cocin Celestial da ke Owo. “Rundunar ‘yan sandan jihar Ondo ba ta da masaniya kan wani hari da aka kai a cocin Celestial da ke Owo,” inji ta. Tawagar mu ta tantance gaskiya ta binciki shafukan sada zumunta na cocin Celestial Church a Owo. Mun kai ga jagorancin Parish 1 da 2, kuma dukkansu sun tabbatar da cewa kwanan nan an nadi bidiyon a Celestial Church of Christ, Parish 2, Owo. Duk da haka, babu wani hari da aka rubuta. A cewar Joseph Oluwasegun, makiyayin cocin Celestial Church of Christ, Owo, Parish 2. Ya ce: “Tsoro ya kama mambobin cocin yayin da suke gudanar da aikin ceto a ranar Lahadi, 5 ga watan Yuni, 2022, sakamakon harbin bindigar da suka yi. sun ji daga Cocin Katolika na St. Francis.” Kafin karar harbe-harbe, ya ce Cocin na cikin yanayi na shagulgula domin bikin girbi na Juvenile Harvest a fadin Cocin Celestial na duniya. Ya tabbatar da cewa ba ‘yan bindiga ne suka kai wa Cocin hari ba kuma kowane dan Cocin yana cikin koshin lafiya. Hukunci A zahiri an dauki hoton bidiyon masu bautar cocin Celestial a Owo a ranar 5 ga watan Yuni. Maganar cewa an kai hari cocin karya ce.